==English==
===Adjective===
'''illiterate'''

# [[Unable]] to [[read]] and [[write]], or having [[little]] [[formal]] [[education]]
# Having [[less]] than an [[expected]] [[standard]] of [[familiarity]] with [[language]] and [[literature]]
# Not [[conforming]] to [[prescribed]] standards of [[speech]] or [[writing]]

====Antonyms====
*[[literate]]

====Related terms====
*[[illiteracy]]

